title: SPECIAL EPISODE: Frank's Interview on Stansberry Radio

description: In a complete role reversal, Frank is interviewed by Aaron Brabham on Stansberry Radio. Frank discusses his latest research on energy stocks, what he sees in the markets for 2012, and what he reads every day.
